程序包 store

类 AppointmentStore

Object
AppointmentStore
public class AppointmentStore extends Object
The AppointmentStore class is responsible for managing the storage and retrieval of Appointment records. It supports adding, removing, updating, and retrieving appointment records and notifying subscribers of additions and removals.

  • 字段详细资料

    • nextId

      private static int nextId
      A static variable to keep track of the next unique identifier for appointments. It is initialized to 0 and increments each time a new appointment is added.

    • appointments

      private static HashMap<String,Appointment> appointments
      A static HashMap to store appointment records. The key is the appointment ID and the value is the appointment record.

    • subscribers

      private static HashSet<ISubscriber> subscribers
      A static HashSet to store subscribers that subscribe to appointment addition and removal notifications.

  • 方法详细资料

    • addRecord

      public static String addRecord(Appointment record)
      Adds a new appointment record to the store and generates an appointment ID for the record. The appointment ID is prefixed with "AP" followed by a 6-digit number. An addition notification will be sent to subscribers.
      参数:
      record - The appointment record to be added
      返回:
      The unique identifier assigned to the appointment

    • removeRecord

      public static void removeRecord(String id)
      Removes an appointment from the store based on the given ID. A removal notification will be sent to subscribers.
      参数:
      id - The ID of the appointment record to be removed

    • updateRecord

      public static void updateRecord(String id, Appointment record)
      Upserts the record of an appointment with the given ID.
      参数:
      id - The ID of the appointment to be upserted
      record - The new appointment record

    • getRecords

      public static List<Appointment> getRecords()
      Retrieves a list of all appointment records.
      返回:
      A list of the appointment records

    • getRecord

      public static Appointment getRecord(String id)
      Retrieves an appointment record by the provided appointment ID.
      参数:
      id - The appointment ID of the appointment to be retrieved
      返回:
      The appointment record associated with the given ID, or null if no such appointment exists

    • subscribe

      public static void subscribe(ISubscriber subscriber)
      Registers a subscriber to appointment addition and removal notifications.
      参数:
      subscriber - The subscriber to register

    • unsubscribe

      public static void unsubscribe(ISubscriber subscriber)
      Unregisters a subscriber from appointment addition and removal notifications.
      参数:
      subscriber - The subscriber to unregister

    • notifySubscribers

      public static void notifySubscribers(Notification notification)
      Notifies all subscribers of an appointment addition or removal.
      参数:
      notification - The notification to be sent to subscribers
